{"tid":2262340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"觀塘警署對開爆水管 附近交通受影響","createTime":"2020-10-29T05:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T07:05:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b4bd00c8ccebb00971bab9c8ff5f5018c81b335b","tid":2262340,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"【10:15】鯉魚門道去油塘，近觀塘警署對開一段快線仍然需要封閉。<br />\n<br />\n早上7時許，觀塘警署對開鯉魚門道與將軍澳交界，十字路口一條地底水管爆竊，路面一帶出現龜裂，水及沙泥不斷從地底湧出，附近一帶行車均受到影響，警員到場封閉部份行車線，水務署派員到場準備搶修。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201029/TZHPCEENJJGUNHVFLDLAE3TIAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201029%2FTZHPCEENJJGUNHVFLDLAE3TIAM%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KijH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=e116426f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201029%2FTZHPCEENJJGUNHVFLDLAE3TIAM%2F&h=a760bb4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201029/TZHPCEENJJGUNHVFLDLAE3TIAM/</a>"},{"pid":"897395a197666c26ca9d67213a4b0984aca354c4","tid":2262340,"uid":76804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"紙皮又要出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fae9066fd4a1a46d3e8bc2bb77211766c2844bc","tid":2262340,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:09:48.000Z","msg":"黑警暴徒(黑暴)又堵路"},{"pid":"b35ed87efb664593da8d96bf389b6a6510c399f2","tid":2262340,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"CONDOM都得啦"},{"pid":"a81cc2b93dd9f0e663c3dcfbe9398f92ff9d2f87","tid":2262340,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwFpv7R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwFpv